high_descs: Move to face the coffee table so that the remote is at the top right corner when you look down at it.
Pick up the candle that's at the center of the table.
Put the candle down on the top left corner of the yellow plate that's closest to you.
Pick up the plate with the candle on it.
Bring the plate over to the console table across the room with the television on it.
Put the plate down on the left side of the shelf beneath the television.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the candle under the TV.

high_descs: Hang a right at the television stand, turn left at the end of the couch and face the glass coffee table on the left at the chair.
Pick up the candle holder with the candle in the middle of the glass table next to the keys.
Put the candle holder with the candle on the gold plate to the left of the statue on the table.
Pick up the plate with the candle holder on the table.
Turn left, hang a right at the couch and walk to the television stand ahead.
Put the plate with the candle holder on the left corner of the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a candle on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward, turn right, walk forward, turn left at end of table, turn left again facing table
Pick up candle off of table
Put candle on plate on table
Pick up candle and plate off of table
Turn left, walk forward, turn right, walk forward to television stand
Put candle and plate on bottom of television stand
anns.task_desc: Move candle from table to television stand
